title: Bullyland Princess Tiana Action Figure
description: Tiana is certainly not a typical fairy tale princess. Her dreams are not about far-away Kingdoms or castles in the clouds, they are about being successful and owning her own restaurant. In all the stress, she has no time for partying, dancing, or love, and the last thing she wants to do is waste her time kissing on men- let alone kissing a frog.
